# Deny by default. Only inputs explicitly needed for the two wasm-pack builds
# and the runtime web trees can enter the build context.
**

!Dockerfile
!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock
!src/
!src/**
!server/
!server/byzorgan-web-server.py

!web/
!web/**
# Generated locally; the container rebuilds these from Rust sources.
web/pkg/
web/pkg-worklet/
# Browser/unit tests and package metadata are not runtime assets.
web/score/tests/
web/score/package.json

!training-prototype/
!training-prototype/*.html
!training-prototype/*.css
!training-prototype/*.js
!training-prototype/manifest.webmanifest
!training-prototype/js/
!training-prototype/js/**
!training-prototype/icons/
!training-prototype/icons/**
!training-prototype/vendor/
!training-prototype/vendor/**
# Only the tracked, hand-made control_satb.musicxml ships baked in. The other
# 4 built-ins are gitignored (see training-prototype/omr/SOURCES.md) and
# NEVER enter any build context, local or CI -- .dockerignore only filters
# what's already present, it can't materialize files git never tracked. They
# reach the image at runtime via a PVC-backed symlink instead (see
# Dockerfile's data/ mount + symlink step). A prior version of this file
# tried `!training-prototype/content/*.musicxml` here, which appeared to work
# on a local build (this dev machine happens to have those gitignored files
# on disk already) but silently did nothing on the real CI build -- confirmed
# broken by deploying and testing before this fix.
!training-prototype/content/
!training-prototype/content/control_satb.musicxml
!training-prototype/samples/
!training-prototype/samples/voices/
!training-prototype/samples/voices/**

# Defense in depth: no OMR code, source corpus, intermediates, verification
# output, or pipeline environment may enter the context. omr/ is excluded
# below, unconditionally -- the catalog and the 4 content built-ins both
# arrive at runtime via the data/ PVC mount, never via the build context.
training-prototype/omr/
training-prototype/omr/**
training-prototype/omr/pdfs/
training-prototype/omr/pages/
training-prototype/omr/gt_crops/
training-prototype/omr/shots/
training-prototype/omr/verify/
training-prototype/omr/out/
training-prototype/omr/.venv/

# Never admit repository metadata, dependency trees, caches, local virtual
# environments, test fixtures, or build output even if a future allow rule is
# accidentally broadened.
.git/
.git/**
**/.git/
**/.git/**
**/node_modules/
**/node_modules/**
target/
target/**
**/target/
**/target/**
**/.venv/
**/.venv/**
**/venv/
**/venv/**
**/__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/**
**/tests/
**/tests/**
**/*fixture*/
**/*fixture*/**
